-Functionality Breakdown for FlaskEcom App:

1. Test if Register functionality actually register New Users into system
   a. Enter all required information to register as anew user
2. Test if Login Functionality actually login
   a. Enter Valid login details (correct email and password)
   b. Enter invalid login details (wrong email and password)
3. Test if Logout Functionality actually logout
   a. Check if a popup shows to confirm if user was logout
4. Test Buying Product functionality
   a. Check if products are added to bought section
   b. Check if amount is deducted when an item is bought
5. Test removing a bought item
   a. Check if an item bought is removed from the bought section
   b. Check if Total amount increases